title: Olympics_Oops clips.avi
description:
A tribute to the Olympics.

     Nude female athletes.

     Sorry- no real nudity here. Just some very short clips from the Barcelona 92 Olympics - womens track and field.

     This clip is from a VHS tape I just happened to be recording at the time. So the quality is not that great. The outfits these runners were wearing were very revealing - and for a change - the cameramen were allowed to be - well - men!
